, sauté <b>5 min\/250°F\/speed 1<b>."},{"content":"Add red peppers, tomatoes, tomato paste and stock paste and water. Place Varoma into position, secure Varoma lid and steam <b>50 min\/Varoma\/\/speed 2<b>."},{"content":"Remove Varoma. Add sweet potatoes into mixing bowl. Place Varoma with beef back into position and insert Varoma tray. Place beans onto Varoma tray, secure Varoma lid and cook a further <b>10 min\/Varoma\/\/speed 2<b>. Remove Varoma and set aside. Transfer chili and beans to covered serving dish."},{"content":"Drain accumulated liquid from short ribs and discard. Place meat into mixing bowl and shred <b>8-10 sec\/\/speed 4<b> until desired consistency is achieved. Transfer to serving dish with chili and stir until combined. Garnish with reserved grated cheese and cilantro leaves. Serve immediately."}],"hintsAndTricks":["Beef stock paste and water can be replaced with 16 oz beef stock.","Adjust consistency with additional beef stock or water if a thinner chili is preferred."],"basicInfo":["medium","15m","1h 25m","6 portions"]}